<link=\"DIRTYWATER\">Polluted Water</link> slowly emits <link=\"CONTAMINATEDOXYGEN\">Polluted Oxygen</link> which accelerates the spread of <link=\"DISEASE\">Disease</link>.\n\nDuplicants will also be <link=\"STRESS\">Stressed</link> by walking through Polluted Water, so I should have my Duplicants clean up spills by (ClickType/clicking) and dragging the <b>Mop Tool</b> {Hotkey/Mop}